title: Excessive Force 2 -Force On Force
description:
Movie Description
In this action shoot-em-up, Los Angeles is under siege by a lethal assassination squad, and it&#039;s time for a beautiful special agent to employ...excessive force.

Credits 
Cast: Stacie Randall 
Director: Jonathan Winfrey 

Synopsis
When a psychotic assassin gathers a vicious rebel army with enough ammunition to instill terror throughout Los Angeles, their first target is special agent Harly Cordell. However, Cordell is a powerful force to contend with, and she will fight not only for her life, but for the innocent lives of millions.
